Ignasi Rib√≥ (born 1971 in Barcelona) is a Catalan writer. He is Doctor of Philosophy from the University of Sussex and holds graduate degrees in Economics, Political Science and Literary Theory. He is the author of the eco-political theory of the habitat-nation, developed in his book "Habitat: The Ecopolitical Nation" (2012). <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ignasi_Rib%C3%B3">Wikipedia</a>
